metadata.name: Intro
metadata.description:
I am very excited to introduce you my new collection «Sati x Editions» first one of 2023.

My intention is to increase my collector base and also reward those who support me. I think editions are a great way to do this, because you can use them as a ticket and get priority in my next projects.  
All editions may differ from each other in style / idea / meaning, because I am an artist and I am always experimenting. 

Thank you for all your support!
